<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Lease Renewal Accepted - 12done.com</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #4F46E5; }
    .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #4F46E5; }
    .content { padding: 30px 0; }
    .success-badge { background: #10B981; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .success-box { background: #ECFDF5; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #10B981; }
    .info-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #A7F3D0; }
    .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .info-label { color: #065F46; }
    .info-value { color: #064E3B; font-weight: 600; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; color: #666; font-size: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">12done.com</div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="success-badge">Renewal Accepted</div>

    <h1>Lease Renewal Has Been Accepted!</h1>

    <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>

    <p>Congratulations! The lease renewal for "{{propertyTitle}}" has been accepted by {{otherPartyName}}.</p>

    <div class="success-box">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">What's Next?</h3>
      <p>A new lease agreement has been created as a draft. The landlord will need to review and activate the new lease before the current one expires.</p>
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Property</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{propertyTitle}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Status</span>
        <span class="info-value">New Lease Draft Created</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">View My Leases</a>
    </p>

    <p>If you have any questions, please reach out to the other party directly through the platform.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The 12done.com Team</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; {{year}} 12done.com. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This is a transactional email regarding your lease on 12done.com.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
